('Residential Supervisor', 'International University of Grand-Bassam', 'manual_extraction_305', '30/03/2026', 'BAC+2', 'International University of Grand-Bassam recrute un Residential Supervisor. Missions : enforce residential rules, handle daily operational problems, prepare and distribute meal tickets, distribute recreational supplies, assist students, control food service delivery, write repairs, report incidents, attend to sick students, record departure/return times, be a resource person for Residential Learning Programs, refer to correct authorities, be available for students, prepare residence for special meetings, encourage physical activity, make daily inspections. Profil : driving license, computer skills (Microsoft Office), ability to collaborate and communicate effectively, ability to work under pressure, effective communication in French and English, Associate Degree in Human services field, education or any related field.', 'VA HAS#2026/08, Residential Supervisor', '', '22527213036402721303457', 'iugbhr@iugb.edu.ci', true, 'GRAND-BASSAM', ARRAY['Supervision', 'Résidence universitaire', 'Accompagnement'], true, 'OUI', '{"title": "Residential Supervisor", "company_name": "International University of Grand-Bassam", "summary": "International University of Grand-Bassam recrute un Residential Supervisor. Missions : enforce residential rules, handle daily operational problems, prepare and distribute meal tickets, distribute recreational supplies, assist students, control food service delivery, write repairs, report incidents, attend to sick students, record departure/return times, be a resource person for Residential Learning Programs, refer to correct authorities, be available for students, prepare residence for special meetings, encourage physical activity, make daily inspections. Profil : driving license, computer skills (Microsoft Office), ability to collaborate and communicate effectively, ability to work under pressure, effective communication in French and English, Associate Degree in Human services field, education or any related field.", "contact": "(225) 27.21.30.36.40 / 27.21.30.34.57", "lettre_motivation": "OUI", "objet": "VA HAS#2026/08, Residential Supervisor", "urls": null, "email": "iugbhr@iugb.edu.ci", "deadline": "30/03/2026", "niveau": "BAC+2", "lieu": "GRAND-BASSAM", "tags": ["Supervision", "R\u00e9sidence universitaire", "Accompagnement"], "salary_range": null}'),
('CHARGE(E) DES OPERATIONS', 'MCH Consulting (pour entreprise cosmétique)', 'manual_extraction_306', '23/03/2026', 'BAC+5, BAC+4', 'Le Cabinet MCH Consulting recrute un(e) Chargé(e) des opérations pour une entreprise cosmétique. Missions : assurer la gestion optimale de la production cosmétique, garantir la qualité, sécurité, environnement, maîtrise des coûts, performance opérationnelle, conformité des pratiques, encadrer les équipes, conduire à la certification ISO 9001, ISO 22716 et ISO 45001, coordonner les activités de l''usine, superviser production, maintenance, achats, moyens généraux, laboratoire, définir des stratégies, superviser la planification de la production, garantir la disponibilité et fiabilité de l''outil de production, analyser les indicateurs de performance, appuyer l''élaboration du CAPEX, garantir la santé, sécurité, hygiène, superviser les projets et travaux, assurer le reporting, veiller au climat social. Profil : expertise technique en cosmétique (formulation, procédés, normes), solides compétences en management et leadership, maîtrise des outils de suivi de production et reporting (SAP, Excel, logiciels KPI), connaissance des réglementations HSE et environnementales, capacité d''analyse et prise de décision rapide, excellentes aptitudes en communication et formation, sens de la discrétion, confidentialité, initiative, anticipation, aisance relationnelle, savoir travailler sous pression, gestion des conflits.', '', '', '', 'mchconsulting@outlook.fr', true, 'Côte d''Ivoire', ARRAY['Production', 'Cosmétique', 'Management', 'ISO', 'HSE'], true, 'OUI (avec prétentions salariales)', '{"title": "CHARGE(E) DES OPERATIONS", "company_name": "MCH Consulting (pour entreprise cosm\u00e9tique)", "summary": "Le Cabinet MCH Consulting recrute un(e) Charg\u00e9(e) des op\u00e9rations pour une entreprise cosm\u00e9tique. Missions : assurer la gestion optimale de la production cosm\u00e9tique, garantir la qualit\u00e9, s\u00e9curit\u00e9, environnement, ma\u