ologies associ\u00e9es, leadership, management d''\u00e9quipe, capacit\u00e9s de n\u00e9gociation, orientation r\u00e9sultats, ma\u00eetrise des outils CRM, anglais courant indispensable, techniques de vente et de n\u00e9gociation, gestion de la relation client, \u00e9laboration d''offres commerciales, sens du relationnel, force de proposition, esprit d''initiative.", "contact": null, "lettre_motivation": null, "objet": null, "urls": null, "email": "cv@topwork.ci", "deadline": "23/03/2026", "niveau": "BAC+5", "lieu": "Abidjan", "tags": ["HVAC", "Commerce", "Management", "Vente B2B"], "salary_range": null}'),
