('ACCOUNTANT II', 'International University of Grand-Bassam', 'manual_extraction_320', '30/03/2026', 'BAC+3', 'International University of Grand-Bassam recrute un Accountant II. Missions : process purchase and sales invoices, monitor customers and suppliers files, receive and verify invoices, monitor settlement periods, assist in monthly reporting, establish and monitor suppliers'' tax exemption, preparation of statements of accounts and financial statements, monitor University asset, assist in annual budget preparation. Profil : confirmed payroll and social statements skills, mastery of Sage, knowledge of students'' management ERP appreciated, ability to anticipate, responsiveness, precision, ability to work in team and under pressure, fluent in French and English, Bachelor''s degree in Accounting with experience in Customer Account Management, experience working with financial services at a university or comparable institution/company.', 'VA ADF#2026/07, Accountant II', '', '2252130364021303457', 'iugbhr@iugb.edu.ci', true, 'ABIDJAN', ARRAY['Comptabilité', 'Finance', 'Sage', 'Bilingue'], true, 'OUI', '{"title": "ACCOUNTANT II", "company_name": "International University of Grand-Bassam", "summary": "International University of Grand-Bassam recrute un Accountant II. Missions : process purchase and sales invoices, monitor customers and suppliers files, receive and verify invoices, monitor settlement periods, assist in monthly reporting, establish and monitor suppliers'' tax exemption, preparation of statements of accounts and financial statements, monitor University asset, assist in annual budget preparation. Profil : confirmed payroll and social statements skills, mastery of Sage, knowledge of students'' management ERP appreciated, ability to anticipate, responsiveness, precision, ability to work in team and under pressure, fluent in French and English, Bachelor''s degree in Accounting with experience in Customer Account Management, experience working with financial services at a university or comparable institution/company.", "contact": "(225) 21.30.36.40 / 21.30.34.57", "lettre_motivation": "OUI", "objet": "VA ADF#2026/07, Accountant II", "urls": null, "email": "iugbhr@iugb.edu.ci", "deadline": "30/03/2026", "niveau": "BAC+3", "lieu": "ABIDJAN", "tags": ["Comptabilit\u00e9", "Finance", "Sage", "Bilingue"], "salary_range": null}'),
